{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/2015/10/clipboardjs-thu-vien-giup-cat-sao-chep-noi-dung-tren-web.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"3ed598f0-94c9-55f4-8586-3da87c287f5e","html":"<p>Clipboard.js là một thư viện vô cùng gọn nhẹ (2kb) giúp bạn dễ dàng cắt hoặc sao chép nội dung trên trang web một cách dễ dàng. Được sử dụng trong các trường hợp bạn muốn người dùng tự động copy dữ liệu vào trong clipboard mà không cần thực hiện thao tác copy hoặc Ctrl + C.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-nogpFtDX4JE/VjNskDinauI/AAAAAAAAFfk/ciSSYDvmaKs/s1600/5ab0a950-5fb4-11e5-9602-e73c0b661883.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Ưu điểm của Clipboard.js là cực kì nhẹ (2kb) và không sử dụng flash.</p>\n<h2 id=\"cài-đặt\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#c%C3%A0i-%C4%91%E1%BA%B7t\" aria-label=\"cài đặt permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Cài đặt</h2>\n<p>Sử dụng npm</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> clipboard --save</code></pre></div>\n<p>Sử dụng bower</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">bower <span class=\"token function\">install</span> clipboard --save</code></pre></div>\n<p>Hoặc bạn có thể download trực tiếp thư viện bằng <a href=\"https://github.com/zenorocha/clipboard.js/archive/master.zip\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">file ZIP tại đây</a> và sử dụng.</p>\n<h2 id=\"cách-sử-dụng\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#c%C3%A1ch-s%E1%BB%AD-d%E1%BB%A5ng\" aria-label=\"cách sử dụng permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Cách sử dụng</h2>\n<p>Thêm thư viện vào trang web bằng thẻ script</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 1. Define some markup --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>btn<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data-clipboard-text</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Copy<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 2. Include library --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>../dist/clipboard.min.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 3. Instantiate clipboard by passing a HTML element --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> btn <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'btn'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> clipboard <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Clipboard</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>btn<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"copy-nội-dung-trong-trang-từ-một-element-khác\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#copy-n%E1%BB%99i-dung-trong-trang-t%E1%BB%AB-m%E1%BB%99t-element-kh%C3%A1c\" aria-label=\"copy nội dung trong trang từ một element khác permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Copy nội dung trong trang từ một element khác</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-FCE1AssAJA8/VjNuQuomESI/AAAAAAAAFfs/4kIq61sAw98/s1600/7df57b9c-6050-11e5-9cd1-fbc51d2fd0a7.png\"></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Target --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>textarea</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>bar<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>Mussum ipsum cacilds...<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>textarea</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Trigger --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>btn<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data-clipboard-action</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>cut<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data-clipboard-target</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#bar<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    Cut to clipboard\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"copy-nội-dung-từ-thuộc-tính\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#copy-n%E1%BB%99i-dung-t%E1%BB%AB-thu%E1%BB%99c-t%C3%ADnh\" aria-label=\"copy nội dung từ thuộc tính permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Copy nội dung từ thuộc tính</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-MLe6ox0NNlw/VjNuj-y-ovI/AAAAAAAAFf0/kw3VM0U1taY/s1600/6e16cf8c-6050-11e5-9883-1c5681f9ec45.png\"></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Trigger --></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>btn<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data-clipboard-text</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Just because you can doesn<span class=\"token punctuation\">'</span>t mean you should — clipboard.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    Copy to clipboard\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Bạn có thể xem thêm các ví dụ và api từ trang chủ của project tại đây: <a href=\"https://github.com/zenorocha/clipboard.js\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://github.com/zenorocha/clipboard.js</a></p>","fields":{"slug":"/2015/10/clipboardjs-thu-vien-giup-cat-sao-chep-noi-dung-tren-web.html","tagSlugs":["/tag/clipboard-js/","/tag/javascript/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2015-10-30T20:22:00.001+07:00","description":"Clipboard.js là một thư viện vô cùng gọn nhẹ (2kb) giúp bạn dễ dàng cắt hoặc sao chép nội dung trên trang web một cách dễ dàng. Được sử dụng trong các trường hợp bạn muốn người dùng tự động copy dữ liệu vào trong clipboard mà không cần thực hiện thao tác copy hoặc Ctrl + C.","tags":["clipboard.js","javascript"],"title":"Clipboard.js - thư viện giúp cắt/sao chép nội dung trên web một cách dễ dàng.","fbCommentUrl":"none"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2015/10/clipboardjs-thu-vien-giup-cat-sao-chep-noi-dung-tren-web.html"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","2672868365","401334301"]}